data.description: Beautiful, well kept home located in a mature, quiet neighborhood. This spacious 4 bedroom is move in ready with high end finishes that include granite counter tops, a large soaker tub, and a beverage chiller. The 3 car garage exemplifies convenience with wifi connectivity.  The living areas are perfect for gathering and family time. The backyard is a pivotal hangout space with a newly built covered patio area, large yard to roam around, and an above ground pool to splash around in the summer heat. Brand new hot water heater, newer garbage disposal, and newer HVAC for main living areas. Schedule your showing while it lasts!
